-------------------------------------------------
Requires:

+ Snort 2 install
+ Snort 2 rules snapshot install

-------------------------------------------------
Edit these files:

setup.sh - configure for your environment.
test.sh - the configs and pcaps you want to test.

-------------------------------------------------
Run this first:

$ ./get_rules.sh

-------------------------------------------------
Then do this (args are cpu, policy, and pcap):

$ ./run.sh 1 connectivity udp1k0

Output is to terminal.

-------------------------------------------------
Or run everything:

$ ./test.sh

Output is in logs/<policy>_<pcap>.log

-------------------------------------------------

